## ⚙️ Setup (Self-Hosting)

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/DuckRaceSociety/duck-race-sniper-bot.git
cd duck-race-sniper-bot
npm install
```

### 2. Create Telegram Bot
- Open [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)
- `/newbot` → follow instructions
- Copy the bot token

### 3. Configure Environment Variables
Create a `.env` file or set in Vercel:
```env
SNIPER_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
```

### 4. Deploy to Vercel
```bash
vercel deploy --prod
```

### 5. Set Webhook
Open in browser:
```
https://your-vercel-url.vercel.app/api/setup-sniper-webhook
```

